\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	i.	}"activity_labels.txt"  -  file containing the numeric codes and descriptive labels of 6 different activities.\
{\listtext	ii.	}\'93features_info.txt"   -  file containing detailed description of where the feature comes from? How the measurements are done on those feature? Overall there are 561 features.\
{\listtext	iii.	}\'93features.txt"        - The complete list of 561 features. \
{\listtext	iv.	}\'93README.txt"       -   The full details of Version 1.0 of the \'93Human Activity Recognition Using Smartphones Dataset\'94\
